<section class="normal-width">
  <p>I began my career as an "iOS developer" but <a href="/blog/building-better-software-by-building-better-teams/">I have learned</a>, <a href="/blog/normalizing-struggle/">I have struggled</a>, and <a href="/blog/perspective-of-the-polyglot/">I have grown</a>. The problems I want to work on <em>now</em> simply cannot be solved with iOS software alone. I am interested in building <em>teams</em> as much as I am interested in building software.</p>
  <p>My <a href="/blog/5-years-of-ios/">first five years</a> and <a href="/blog/5-more-years-of-building-software/">my second five years</a> of professional software development are openly documented, if you want an in-depth look.</p>
