  <p>I grew up playing music but stopped after high school. Years later, <a href="https://ashfurrow.com/blog/learning-guitar/">I picked up a guitar for the first time</a> and <a href="https://ashfurrow.com/blog/music-is-back/">rediscovered</a> my love of music. Some friends of mine had formed a cover band of The Weakerthans. Sadly, COVID hit just before our first performance.</p>
